PLACEHOLDER – Replace with your Apple Pass Type ID certificate (PEM format)

Steps:
  1. Export your certificate from Keychain Access (or download from Apple Developer portal)
     as a .cer (DER) file.
  2. Convert:  openssl x509 -inform DER -in pass.cer -out pass_cert.pem
  3. Replace this file with the resulting pass_cert.pem

The file must start with:
  -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
  ...
  -----END CERTIFICATE-----

Note: This is the PUBLIC certificate only — never place the private key here.
      The private key stays in the APPLE_PASS_KEY_PEM environment variable.
